@f image
@a M.A. Windhouwer
@* The image module

The current version is just a very subtype of the url ADT.
Future extensions include specialized constructors, the
ability to specify a limited amount of meta-data (e.g.
width and height) and a local representant (i.e. an icon).

@m
.MODULE image;

   .USE url; 

	.ATOM image = url;
	.END;

.END image;
